{"tid":564102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(支共垃圾中文) cctvb 我屌你老母啦","createTime":"2018-02-17T15:11:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T15:34:54.000Z","uid":54337,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1caeab1e46d966923a18a013181ccbac7b25fe3e","tid":564102,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T15:11:08.000Z","msg":"睇新聞，報導南泡冬奧比賽，聽到 &ldquo;花樣滑冰&rdquo; ，我耳都側埋。<br />\n我樣你個老母個臭西，滑你老母呀啦仆街冚家剷。<br />\n<br />\n九七前，報體育新聞，係叫做：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">花式溜冰</span></strong><br />\nCctvb，你仆街冚家剷啦，我屌你老母。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，越來越垃圾支共中文入侵香港，例如：<br />\n<br />\n九七前，趨勢<br />\n九七淪陷後，勢頭<br />\n<br />\n九七前，頭皮<br />\n九七淪陷後，頭屑<br />\n<br />\n九七前，脫髮<br />\n九七淪陷後，掉髮<br />\n<br />\n九七前，山泥傾瀉<br />\n九七淪陷後，滑坡/泥石流/山體崩滑<br />\n<br />\n九七前，新年<br />\n九七淪陷後，春節<br />\n<br />\n九七前，開幕禮<br />\n九七淪陷後，開幕式<br />\n<br />\n唉，香港玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b71ca392b26c1c3ad96487f019addf14c30e3d","tid":564102,"uid":162424,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T15:12:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"31f849b6dc5597d1595e3031dc4a0b8aab919f19","tid":564102,"uid":41508,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T15:13:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e2b18fab6cb72a06dc02177c587c9a957dd4023a","tid":564102,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T15:15:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>九七前：英屬香港<br />\n九七淪陷後：枣果腥枧</strong></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"fb514478434bc6a191eef5e65da1e3648d5564be","tid":564102,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T15:23:33.000Z","msg":"九七前，心照啦/心照不宣<br />\n九七淪陷後，你懂的<br />\n<br />\n我懂你老母塊臭西啦，仆街大陸佬"},{"pid":"a16f9ad291e3688aa251ed0cb14bbe1fdf426de0","tid":564102,"uid":140802,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T15:34:54.000Z","msg":"前排佢地好鍾意講<br />\n加乜撚野大力度<img src=\"/asset